&lt;p&gt;An opportunity has arisen for an experienced Team Administrator to join the Enhanced Care Ward at the Radbourne Unit for a Fixed Term Contract of 11 months to cover a secondment.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Enhanced Care Ward is a ten-bedded, mixed-sex ward which provides care to individuals with complex physical and mental health needs.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The successful candidate will be expected to provide admin support to the Ward Manager and inpatient team.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will be provided with an initial training programme and receive regular supervision.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further information please contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Kerby Walker, Senior Nurse&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;or&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Hollie Grief, Lead Nurse&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;ECW on 01332 623803.&lt;/p&gt;
